{"tid":1872931,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"長者不滿政府抗疫措施 刪與林鄭月娥合照","createTime":"2020-02-10T10:42:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T13:52:26.000Z","uid":212626,"like":448,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"90141635fa03e4af85179de21ef3d0a5a9d727d1","tid":1872931,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T10:42:06.000Z","msg":"【長者不滿政府抗疫措施　刪與林鄭月娥合照】<br />\n<br />\n70歲的陳女士稱近日多次排隊購買口罩失敗，不滿政府未有提供協助。她向傳媒展示手機內一張，2017年她與當時參選特首的林鄭月娥的合照，稱曾經期望林鄭月娥成為一位好特首，但如今認為林鄭月娥比之前幾任更差，令她非常失望，所以要刪掉兩人的合照。<br />\n<br />\n#香港電台 #林鄭月娥 #合照 #口罩 #新型肺炎 #新型冠狀病毒<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/videos/188226665727735/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRTHKVNEWS%2Fvideos%2F188226665727735%2F&d=nNI0xXmu%2FnmsXsjxjv7MVZnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=1da5a8a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/videos/188226665727735/</a>"},{"pid":"de717575c2da0db0e66d6181eb8ab954ae294c9b","tid":1872931,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T10:43:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7c52ef76e29b47710110311ca7268e719d14776","tid":1872931,"uid":25468,"like":67,"dislike":2,"score":65,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T10:44:38.000Z","msg":"公開處刑 ?"},{"pid":"12fcb187660f4b011bf32ec06f7d7968fe67842a","tid":1872931,"uid":19527,"like":201,"dislike":4,"score":197,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T10:45:48.000Z","msg":"放心啦阿嬸，之後幾個會更差"},{"pid":"6fb56592795d010d894cc5de49ce97675740e0a5","tid":1872931,"uid":61882,"like":127,"dislike":1,"score":126,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T10:46:21.000Z","msg":"淨係剷張相有咩用吖<br />\n要冚家剷先掂架阿姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84ff66423fd31ff5f90184e43434ea675b89a09b","tid":1872931,"uid":256019,"like":96,"dislike":2,"score":94,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T10:47:45.000Z","msg":"阿嬸有冇諗過自己都冇份搞成今日局面？唔好講到唔關自己事咁！<img src=\"/a